Project Title : 
Aliexpress product scraper

Project Overview:

Scrap selected Product from aliExpress manage them and export the WooComerce and shopify 

Project Description 

a User can install a chrome extention 

user create an account and autanticate

user select products to export 

then click submit to upload them in the application dashboead

application features:
the application offer a set of features like:
modify imported product (title /desccription/ Price)
export as json /xls /xml
export to woocomerce
export to shopify
export to youcan


phase 1 Of the Project:

create Api that search a product and scrap its details


phase 2 :

-create chrome extention that enable user to select product (select Id) 
and save it into a list

phase 3

integrate the api into the chrome exention


phase 4: 
User auth,
store product in db and manage them 
export to json

phase 5 :

export to woocomerce /shopify/youcan

